        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "The executioner paused and shook his head with an expression of despair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"Tell me about it,\" said the monk, who, sitting on the foot of the bed, began to be interested in a story so strangely introduced.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"Ah!\" cried the dying man, with all the effusiveness of a grief declared after long suppression, \"ah!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "All have forgiven me, some have even loved me; but I think that God has not pardoned me, for the memory of that execution pursues me constantly and every night I see that woman's ghost rising before me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"A woman!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "I am an assassin, then, and not an officer of justice!\" and he closed his eyes with a groan.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "The monk doubtless feared that he would die without saying more, for he exclaimed eagerly:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"Delirium!\" murmured the monk, shaking his head.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "The executioner opened his eyes, turned toward the young man and grasped his arm.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"'Delirium,'\" he repeated; \"'delirium,' do you say?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Oh, no! I remember too well.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "After being the instrument of human justice I aspired to be that of the justice of God.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Speak,\" said the monk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"It was at night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "A man came to me and showed me an order and I followed him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Four other noblemen awaited me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "They led me away masked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_121402_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/121402/1544_121402_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "I reserved the right of refusing if the office they required of me should seem unjust.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "twenty one",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "THE SKY LINE WIDENS",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "While she was wondering how this could be successfully accomplished, some of the other girls were cogitating as to how they could meander through the four years and come out at the end knowing no more than at the beginning.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "This would seem a difficult, well nigh an impossible task, but it can be achieved, and has been, at other seats of learning than modest little Wareham.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "One book was as bad as another in her eyes, and she could have seen the libraries of the world sinking into ocean depths and have eaten her dinner cheerfully the while; but matters assumed a different complexion when she was sent to Edgewood and Rebecca to Wareham.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Another week passed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Her color faded, and her appetite (at table) dwindled almost to nothing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Wareham was a pretty village with a broad main street shaded by great maples and elms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "There was an opportunity for a deal of foolish and imprudent behavior, but on the whole surprisingly little advantage was taken of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1544_140055_000008_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1544/140055/1544_140055_000008_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "She had merry eyes, a somewhat too plump figure for her years, and was popularly supposed to have a fascinating way with her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
