        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"You'll like her; she writes,\" whispered Huldah to Rebecca the first morning at prayers, where the faculty sat in an imposing row on the front seats.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
