        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "This height of achievement made Rebecca somewhat shy of her, but she looked her admiration; something that most of the class could never do with the unsatisfactory organs of vision given them by Mother Nature.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
