        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "The old were for the most part either in old uniforms of the nobility, buttoned up closely, with spurs and hats, or in their own special naval, cavalry, infantry, or official uniforms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
