        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Hliustov would not agree to go with his district to ask Snetkov to stand, while Sviazhsky was persuading him to do so, and Sergey Ivanovitch was approving of the plan.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
