        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "\"One district's enough, and Sviazhsky's obviously of the opposition,\" he said, words evidently intelligible to all except Levin.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
