        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "I suppose you're converted, eh?\" he added, turning to Levin and drawing his arm through his.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
