        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "Now eight districts had agreed to call upon him: if two refused to do so, Snetkov might decline to stand at all; and then the old party might choose another of their party, which would throw them completely out in their reckoning.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
