        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "But if only one district, Sviazhsky's, did not call upon him to stand, Snetkov would let himself be balloted for.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
