        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1544",
        "content": "They were even, some of them, going to vote for him, and purposely to let him get a good many votes, so that the enemy might be thrown off the scent, and when a candidate of the other side was put up, they too might give him some votes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
